text: Agdistis cypriota is a moth in the family Pterophoridae. It is known from Cyprus, TurkeyNachrichtenblatt der Bayerischen Entomologen and Tunisia.Nachrichtenblatt der Bayerischen Entomologen ==References== Category:Agdistinae Category:Moths of Europe Category:Moths described in 1983
